      "content": "that's interesting. can u elaborate on the fast-twitch/slow-twitch thing? like do specific groups just have a naturally higher ceiling for things like sprinting vs long distance? i'm just trying to understand if there's a predictable way to group people for certain drills based on their background so i don't waste anyone's time.",
